span.para: 如果不存在所请求的类型的默认文件夹，具体取决于类型，可以创建 Outlook 并返回文件夹，或可能会引发错误。例如，如果 olFolderManagedEmail 指定为 FolderType，但是尚未部署托管文件夹组，Outlook 将引发错误。

If the default folder of the requested type does not exist, depending on the type, Outlook may create and return the folder, or may raise an error. For example, if olFolderManagedEmail is specified as the FolderType but the Managed Folders group has not been deployed, then Outlook raises an error.
